obs.ontologyAccess.bean
Class BioPortalFullConceptBean

java.lang.Object
  obs.ontologyAccess.bean.BioPortalLightConceptBean
      obs.ontologyAccess.bean.BioPortalFullConceptBean

public class BioPortalFullConceptBean
extends BioPortalLightConceptBean

This class is a JavaBean representation of a full concept bean returned by BioPortal. This bean are created by hitting the URL: http://rest.bioontology.org/bioportal/rest/concepts/{localOntologyID}/{BPConceptID}
For instance: http://rest.bioontology.org/bioportal/rest/concepts/38677/DOID:1909
We extract from that URL only the information we need to implement the BioPortalAccessTool.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Clement Jonquet
